<h2 class="bold font-l">JJBA: Phantom Blood</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
In one of his many attempts to torment Jonathan Joestar, Dio Brando goes after Erina, JoJo's girlfriend, and steals her first kiss in a way only a dastardly villain like him would do. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SacredFirstKiss" class='trope-example-link'>Sacred First Kiss</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="tduw4a" data-video-descrip="DIO shows Jonathan his true colors by kicking his dog." data-video-title="DIO the Invader" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/tduw4a_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/tduw4a.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/KickTheDog" data-video-tropename="Kick the Dog" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Franchise/JojosBizarreAdventure,Manga/JojosBizarreAdventurePhantomBlood" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/tduw4a.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">DIO the Invader</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="jk51ft" data-video-descrip="As promised, DIO didn't lay a finger on the baby." data-video-title="&quot;The irony is lost on you.&quot;" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/jk51ft_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/jk51ft.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/TranshumanTreachery" data-video-tropename="Transhuman Treachery" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Franchise/JojosBizarreAdventure,Manga/JojosBizarreAdventurePhantomBlood" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/jk51ft.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">"The irony is l...</span></p>
</a>
